In [127]:
df['Complaint_Category'] = np.where(df['Complaint_Category'].str.contains('Internet|Speed|wifi|Access|Throttling|throt|Broadband|Cable|connection|DSL|modem|ip|ISP',case=False,regex=True), 'Internet',
         np.where(df['Complaint_Category'].str.contains('\$|Price|Pricing|Cost|Payment|Charg|pay|Bill|Billing|Rate|Contract|fee',case=False,regex=True), 'Billing',
         np.where(df['Complaint_Category'].str.contains('Service|Cap|usage|Data|Customer|switch|wait|support|TV|avail|network|cramming',case=False,regex=True), 'Network',
         np.where(df['Complaint_Category'].str.contains('Customer|complaint|breach|bully|False|fed up',case=False,regex=True), 'Grievance',
         np.where(df['Complaint_Category'].str.contains('email',case=False,regex=True), 'Email',
         np.where(df['Complaint_Category'].str.contains('outage',case=False,regex=True), 'Outages',
         'Other'))))))
